high_descs: Turn right and head towards the door on the left, then go through it and turn right into the kitchen area, approaching the sink.
Pick up the knife from the drainboard next to the sink.
Exit this area the way you came in and go right through the hall, taking the last door on the left and going towards the potato to the right.
Slice the potato on the desk.
Exit this room how you came in, turn right and go straight down the hall to get back to the kitchen area, going to the microwave in the corner.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Return to the desk where you sliced the potato.
Pick up one potato slice.
Exit this room how you came in and turn left into the room with the sink.
Rinse off the potato slice with water and pick the potato back up.
Return to the microwave where you placed the knife.
Put the potato slice into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, wash one slice inside a sink, and place the potato slice in a microwave.
